      "id": "issue-checkpoint",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Issue #139 checkpoint\n\nTools survive HTTP decode + gateway. Silent failure at **provider translation**.\n\nNative structs omit tools; slim wrappers omit top-level tools; OpenAI stream drops assistant ToolCalls + deltas.\n\nMCP loop never fires â†’ text-only, no error.\n\n**Probes:** decode â†’ pre-provider req â†’ outbound HTTP body â†’ raw API response â†’ StreamChunk.Delta.ToolCalls",
      "x": -1400,
      "y": 1380,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 280,
      "color": "3"
    }
